sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend (Dashboard)
    participant BE as Backend (Python)
    participant NIC as Network Interface

    Note over FE, BE: 1. Initialization
    FE->>BE: Start Sniffing (Interface ID)
    BE->>NIC: Open Socket
    
    Note over BE, NIC: 2. Real-Time Processing
    loop Every Packet
        NIC->>BE: Raw Packet
        Note over BE: Group by 5-tuple
        Note over BE: Check: Is this Packet #8?
        
        rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
            Note over BE: If Yes: Run Random Forest
            BE->>FE: WebSocket: { "app": "Video", "src": "192.168.1.5" }
        end
    end

    Note over FE: 3. UI Update
    FE->>FE: Update Pie Chart
    FE->>FE: Add Row to Log